    <div class="policy-card">
      <span class="updated-tag"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i> Last updated: 23 May 2026</span>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>1. Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>At Shop2Bhutan, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, who we share it with, and the choices you have regarding your information.</p>
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-lock" style="margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-database" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <table class="data-table">
        <tr>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Examples</th>
          <th>How We Collect</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Contact Info</strong></td>
          <td>Name, WhatsApp number, email address</td>
          <td>Order form, WhatsApp chat</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Delivery Info</strong></td>
          <td>Delivery address, city, landmark</td>
          <td>Order form</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Order Details</strong></td>
          <td>Product links, descriptions, screenshots, quantities</td>
          <td>Order form, file upload, WhatsApp</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Payment Info</strong></td>
          <td>Payment method selected, transaction references</td>
          <td>WhatsApp confirmation</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Usage Data</strong></td>
          <td>IP address, browser type, pages visited</td>
          <td>Website cookies & logs</td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your personal data strictly for the following purposes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Order processing:</strong> To communicate with you about your order, confirm product details, and arrange delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>Delivery:</strong> To share your address and contact number with our delivery personnel so they can reach you.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment:</strong> To confirm payment status and send reminders for partial payment balances.</li>
        <li><strong>Customer support:</strong> To respond to inquiries, refund requests, and complaints via WhatsApp.</li>
        <li><strong>Service improvement:</strong> To analyse order patterns and improve our procurement and delivery operations.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal compliance:</strong> To comply with applicable laws, regulations, or lawful requests from authorities.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user-group" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>4. Who We Share Data With</h2>
      <p>We keep your data within our operational team. Limited sharing occurs only with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Delivery partners:</strong> Your name, phone number, and address are shared with the individual responsible for delivering your order. They are instructed to use this information solely for delivery purposes.</li>
        <li><strong>Indian sellers (minimal):</strong> In rare cases where a seller requires recipient contact for delivery within India (before we collect from Jaigaon), we may provide a contact number. No Bhutan address is shared with Indian sellers.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal authorities:</strong> If required by law, court order, or to protect our rights and safety.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-cookie-bite" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>5. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
      <p>Our website uses minimal cookies for functionality:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> To keep your form progress saved if you leave and return.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> We may use basic analytics to understand website traffic (no personal identification).</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect form auto-save functionality.</p>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-clock-rotate-left" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes outlined in this policy:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Active orders:</strong> Retained until delivery is completed and any post-delivery issues are resolved (up to 30 days).</li>
        <li><strong>Order history:</strong> Retained for 12 months to assist with repeat orders, refunds, and dispute resolution.</li>
        <li><strong>Financial records:</strong> Retained for 3 years as required by applicable tax and accounting regulations.</li>
        <li><strong>After retention period:</strong> Personal identifiers are deleted or anonymized. Aggregated, non-identifiable data may be kept for business analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>7. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Order data is stored on secured servers with access limited to authorized personnel only.</li>
        <li>WhatsApp communications are protected by WhatsApp's end-to-end encryption.</li>
        <li>We do not store bank account details, card numbers, or mobile wallet PINs.</li>
        <li>While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your data, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-hand" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data, subject to legal retention requirements.</li>
        <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to certain types of processing (e.g., analytics).</li>
        <li><strong>Withdrawal of consent:</strong> If you previously consented to data use, you may withdraw it at any time.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us via WhatsApp at <strong>+975 77113302</strong>. We will respond within 7 business days.</p>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-child-reaching" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our service is not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal data from minors. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately so we can delete the data.</p>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-globe" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>10. Cross-Border Data Transfers</h2>
      <p>Because we procure products from India, limited operational data (such as product links and screenshots) is viewed on devices or systems that may process data outside Bhutan. However, your personal contact and address information remains stored and processed within our Bhutan-based operations unless required for delivery coordination.</p>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. The updated version will be posted on this page with a revised date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>

      <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope" style="color:var(--primary); margin-right:0.5rem;"></i>12. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, concerns, or complaints about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please reach out:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +975 77113302</li>
        <li><strong>Business Name:</strong> Shop2Bhutan</li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> Thimphu, Bhutan</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We take privacy seriously and will make every effort to address your concerns promptly and fairly.</p>
